{"word":"ἐπίγνωσις","slug":"ἐπίγνωσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπίγνωσις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γινώσκω\">γινώσκω</a></el>] <b>knowledge,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> connotation of personal acquaintance, insight, or perception <b><a href='B:520 1:28'>Ro 1:28</a></b> (<el>ϑεὸν ἔχειν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> ἐ.</el> to be constantly aware of God); <b><a href='B:520 3:20'>3:20</a>; <a href='B:560 1:17'>Eph 1:17</a>; <a href='B:570 1:9'>Phil 1:9</a>; <a href='B:580 1:9'>Col 1:9f</a>; <a href='B:610 2:4'>1 Ti 2:4</a>; <a href='B:620 2:25'>2 Ti 2:25</a>; <a href='B:630 1:1'>Tit 1:1</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 6</a>; <a href='B:650 10:26'>Hb 10:26</a>; <a href='B:680 1:2'>2 Pt 1:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιγνούς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιγνώσομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}